-- Giants to Play Vikings in Detroit After Metrodome Roof Caves In Under Snow
-- B y   D e x   M c L u s k e y
-- 2010-12-12T17:05:24Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-12/giants-to-play-vikings-in-detroit-after-metrodome-roof-caves-in-under-snow.html
The Minnesota Vikings will play the
New York Giants at Ford Field in Detroit tomorrow after the roof
at the Metrodome in Minneapolis collapsed today during a
snowstorm.  The game will begin at 7:20 p.m. eastern time, the National
Football Legue said in its website.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dex McLuskey at 
 dmcluskey@bloomberg.net  